{"ID":"20260305082131-y90h5nu","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082131-y90h5nu","title":"README","type":"doc","updated":"20260305091155"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305090254-18tny8g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305090254-18tny8g","updated":"20260305091155"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"{\n  \"editOperations\": [\n    {\n      \"operationType\": \"insert\",\n      \"blockId\": \"20260305082130-86a401l\",\n      \"position\": \"before\",\n      \"newContent\": \"# 学习笔记仓库\\n\\n## 概述\\n\\n这是一个个人学习笔记仓库，主要包含计算机科学、数学等学科的课程笔记和读书笔记。笔记使用思源笔记格式编写，内容涵盖C++程序设计、概率论与数理统计等多个领域。\\n\\n## 目录结构\\n\\n### 1. C++程序设计\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"基础"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：C++编程基础概念\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"类与对象"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：面向对象编程的核心概念\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"继承"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：类的继承机制\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"多态与虚函数"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：运行时多态的实现\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"模板"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：泛型编程\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"异常处理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：错误处理机制\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"标准库"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：C++标准库的使用\\n\\n### 2. 概率论与数理统计\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"大数定律与中心极限定理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\\n  - 切比雪夫大数定律\\n  - 辛钦大数定律\\n  - 伯努利大数定律\\n  - 中心极限定理（Lévy-Lindeberg、De Moivre-Laplace、Liapunov）\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"数理统计"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\\n  - 总体与样本\\n  - 抽样分布（χ²分布、t分布、F分布）\\n  - 正态总体统计量\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"参数估计"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\\n  - 点估计（矩估计、极大似然估计）\\n  - 估计量评选标准（无偏性、有效性、一致性）\\n  - 区间估计\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"假设检验"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\\n  - 参数假设检验\\n  - 正态总体均值检验\\n  - 正态总体方差检验\\n\\n### 3. 其他笔记\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"大学物理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：物理学科笔记（内容待完善）\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"离散数学"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：离散数学笔记（内容待完善）\\n- "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Clippings"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：摘录和剪贴内容\\n\\n## 笔记特点\\n\\n1. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"结构化组织"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：每个主题都有清晰的层级结构\\n2. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"数学公式支持"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：使用LaTeX格式的数学公式\\n3. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"详细推导"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：包含定理证明和公式推导过程\\n4. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实例说明"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：通过具体例子解释抽象概念\\n5. "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"交叉引用"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：支持文档间的引用链接\\n\\n## 使用说明\\n\\n1. 笔记使用思源笔记的kramdown格式\\n2. 包含丰富的数学公式和统计图表\\n3. 每个文档都有完整的元数据（标签、分类等）\\n4. 支持块级引用和文档链接\\n\\n## 更新计划\\n\\n- [ ] 完善大学物理笔记内容\\n- [ ] 完善离散数学笔记内容\\n- [ ] 添加更多编程语言笔记\\n- [ ] 整理算法与数据结构笔记\\n\\n## 标签分类\\n\\n- 读书笔记\\n- 课程笔记\\n- 计算机科学\\n- 数学\\n- 概率统计\\n- C++程序设计\\n\\n---\\n\\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"最后更新：2026年3月5日"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"笔记持续更新中..."},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}]}]}